title: Pants Optional Critmas!
description: CRITMASTIME IS HERE! It's not December but WHO CARES?! Brian Wayne Foster is incognito at an undisclosed location so Taliesin Jaffe, Marisha Ray, Laura Bailey, Matt Mercer, and Liam O'Brien take over and host a casual Critmas! Pants are optional.
